<view class="page">
  <view class="header-section">
    <view class="logo-wrapper">
      <view class="logo-icon">
        <text class="logo-text">闲置</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <text class="app-name">闲置社区</text>
    <text class="app-version">v1.0.0</text>
  </view>

  <view class="info-section">
    <view class="info-card">
      <view class="info-item">
        <text class="info-label">应用介绍</text>
        <text class="info-value">闲置社区是一个专注于本地社区的二手闲置品交易平台，帮助邻居们互相分享闲置物品，让资源流动起来。</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="info-card">
      <view class="info-item">
        <text class="info-label">主要功能</text>
        <view class="feature-list">
          <view class="feature-item">
            <text class="feature-dot">•</text>
            <text class="feature-text">发布闲置品，快速变现</text>
          </view>
          <view class="feature-item">
            <text class="feature-dot">•</text>
            <text class="feature-text">浏览附近闲置，发现好物</text>
          </view>
          <view class="feature-item">
            <text class="feature-dot">•</text>
            <text class="feature-text">分类筛选，精准查找</text>
          </view>
          <view class="feature-item">
            <text class="feature-dot">•</text>
            <text class="feature-text">收藏喜欢，随时查看</text>
          </view>
          <view class="feature-item">
            <text class="feature-dot">•</text>
            <text class="feature-text">距离展示，方便自提</text>
          </view>
          <view class="feature-item">
            <text class="feature-dot">•</text>
            <text class="feature-text">多种联系方式，便捷沟通</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="info-card">
      <view class="info-item">
        <text class="info-label">联系我们</text>
        <text class="info-value">如有任何问题或建议，欢迎通过以下方式联系我们：</text>
        <view class="contact-list">
          <view class="contact-item" bindtap="copyWechat">
            <text class="contact-icon">💬</text>
            <view class="contact-info">
              <text class="contact-label">微信号</text>
              <text class="contact-value">xianzhi_community</text>
            </view>
            <text class="copy-btn">复制</text>
          </view>
          <view class="contact-item" bindtap="makePhoneCall">
            <text class="contact-icon">📞</text>
            <view class="contact-info">
              <text class="contact-label">客服电话</text>
              <text class="contact-value">400-123-4567</text>
            </view>
            <text class="contact-arrow">></text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="info-card">
      <view class="info-item">
        <text class="info-label">版权声明</text>
        <text class="info-value">© 2024 闲置社区 版权所有</text>
        <text class="info-value">本平台仅供信息展示，交易请双方自行核实，注意交易安全。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="footer-section">
    <text class="footer-text">让闲置流动起来</text>
    <text class="footer-copyright">Powered by 闲置社区</text>
  </view>
</view>
